summary: This file removes the puzzle door from Fahlbtharz. Thats the glitchy infuriating one that you cannot open without dumping half an hour into.
descriptionHtml: I hate this d@#m door so much that I created a mod just to deal with it. If you don\'t want to spend half an hour to an hour attempting to open this door despite clearly hitting the activators then install this mod. It will allow you to bypass the puzzle by deleting the doorway blocking your path.
author: jcdenton2012
